## 2. applookup Fields

`applookup/select` fields store **full URLs** to related records.

### URL Format
```
https://my.living-apps.de/rest/apps/{app_id}/records/{record_id}
```

### ⚠️ CRITICAL: Always use extractRecordId()

```typescript
